 English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/cellSpacing\"><code>cellSpacing</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/frame\"><code>frame</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/rows\"><code>rows</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/rules\"><code>rules</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/summary\"><code>summary</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/tBodies\"><code>tBodies</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/tFoot\"><code>tFoot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/tHead\"><code>tHead</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/createCaption\"><code>createCaption()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/createTBody\"><code>createTBody()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/createTFoot\"><code>createTFoot()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/createTHead\"><code>createTHead()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/deleteCaption\"><code>deleteCaption()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/deleteRow\"><code>deleteRow()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/deleteTFoot\"><code>deleteTFoot()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/deleteTHead\"><code>deleteTHead()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement/insertRow\"><code>insertRow()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html_table_.ec.9a.94.ec.86.8c_.ec.9d.b8.ed.84.b0.ed.8e.98.ec.9d.b4.ec.8a.a4","title":"HTML Table 요소 인터페이스","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>table</code> 개체는 (상속으로 이용할 수 있는 정규 <a href=\"ko/DOM/element\">element</a> 개체 인터페이스 외에) HTML 표의 layout과 presentation을 다루는 특수 프로퍼티와 메소드를 제공하는 <code><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-HTML/html.html#ID-64060425\" rel=\" noopener\">HTMLTableElement</a></code> 인터페이스를 내놓습니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ed.94.84.eb.a1.9c.ed.8d.bc.ed.8b.b0","title":"프로퍼티","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect1\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.caption\">table.caption</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>caption</b>은 표 caption을 반환합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect2\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.tHead\">table.tHead</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>tHead</b>는 표 head를 반환합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect3\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.tFoot\">table.tFoot</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>tFoot</b>은 표 footer를 반환합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect4\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.rows\">table.rows</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>rows</b>는 표의 줄(row)을 반환합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect5\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.tBodies\">table.tBodies</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>tBodies</b>는 표 body를 반환합니다.</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect6\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.align\">table.align</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>align</b>은 표 정렬을 get/set합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect7\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.bgColor\">table.bgColor</a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg>&nbsp;</dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>bgColor</b>는 표의 배경색을 get/set합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect8\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.border\">table.border</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>border</b>는 표 border를 get/set합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect9\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.cellPadding\">table.cellPadding</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>cellPadding</b>은 cell padding을 get/set합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect10\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.cellSpacing\">table.cellSpacing</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>cellSpacing</b>은 표 주변 spacing을 get/set합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect11\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.frame\">table.frame</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>frame</b>은 표 어느 쪽이 border를 가질 지를 지정합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect12\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.rules\">table.rules</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>rules</b>는 안쪽 border가 보일 지를 지정합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect13\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.summary\">table.summary</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>summary</b>는 표 요약을 get/set합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect14\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.width\">table.width</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>width</b>는 표 너비를 get/set합니다.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.a9.94.ec.86.8c.eb.93.9c","title":"메소드","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect15\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.createTHead\">table.createTHead</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>createTHead</b>는 표 header를 만듭니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect16\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.deleteTHead\">table.deleteTHead</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>deleteTHead</b>는 표 header를 없앱니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect17\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.createTFoot\">table.createTFoot</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>createTFoot</b>은 표 footer를 만듭니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect18\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.deleteTFoot\">table.deleteTFoot</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>deleteTFoot</b>은 표 footer를 없앱니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect19\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.createCaption\">table.createCaption</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>createCaption</b>는 표에 새 caption을 만듭니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect20\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.deleteCaption\">table.deleteCaption</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>deleteCaption</b>은 표 caption을 없앱니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect21\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.insertRow\">table.insertRow</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>insertRow</b>는 새 줄을 삽입합니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect22\">\n  <a href=\"ko/DOM/table.deleteRow\">table.deleteRow</a></dt>\n <dd>\n  <b>deleteRow</b>는 줄을 없앱니다.</dd>\n</dl>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"table 개체는 (상속으로 이용할 수 있는 정규 element 개체 인터페이스 외에) HTML 표의 layout과 presentation을 다루는 특수 프로퍼티와 메소드를 제공하는 HTMLTableElement 인터페이스를 내놓습니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLTableElement","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"HTMLTableElement","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"table","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"table","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLTableElement","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTMLTableElement","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"HTMLTableElement","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTMLTableElement","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/htmltableelement","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/htmltableelement/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement","title":"table"}],"pageTitle":"table - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}